{"tid":1793361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警眼中只要冇即時殺死人，就係最低武力","createTime":"2019-12-22T10:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T11:05:17.000Z","uid":127929,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3164f1479b2c412bd7b0c4bd63ba29474936069c","tid":1793361,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"所以可以隨便拎住實彈槍，指住任何唔順眼既人，開左槍冇即時殺死人都係最低武力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUwCLPk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUwCLPk.png&h=1a6d54d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而7.21元朗黑社會就係得到黑警容許之下既恐怖襲擊黎，所以話之拎住開山刀都冇事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teSBSLT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteSBSLT.gif&h=a25b7835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqVzfha.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqVzfha.gif&h=88e16dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我想講，黑警呢啲係<span style=\"color: red;\">完全錯誤，絕對唔合理</span>既而且係犯法既行為！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家到呢一刻都覺得係<span style=\"color: red;\">預左喇，唔意外，反正香港冇法治</span>既話，你就同上一代個班遇到支共打壓冇膽唔敢反抗出聲，麻木左既人一撚樣，害死香港人同我地既下一代！<br />\n<br />\n相信大家仲記得7.1係立法會個次既事，香港人要出聲，<span style=\"color: red;\">一輸就真係玩撚完！</span>"},{"pid":"6ccbd5e23bc54f2afe4742392a61d673e5528271","tid":1793361,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解1223稅局冇人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.